DNS
---

to know ip address use host cmd
cmd > host www.megacorp.com

to automate
-----------


list.txt
------
www
ftp
mail
router
proxy


cmd > for ip in $(cat list.txt) ; do host $ip.megacrop.com ; done

for dnszone tansfer
-----------------
cmd > host -t ns websiteaddress.me 
cmd > host -l websiteaddres.me nameserverwegotfromabovecmd

(or)

cmd > dig wesiteaddress.me -t ns
cmd > dig axfr wesiteaddress.me @nameserver

(or)

cmd > dnsrecon -d websitedomain.com -t axfr

